{
    "id": "aquaria/sponge-filter",
    "title": "Install a sponge filter",
    "description": "Add gentle filtration to keep your tank clean without harming shrimp.",
    "image": "/assets/quests/install_sponge_filter_aquarium.jpg",
    "npc": "/assets/npc/vega.jpg",
    "start": "start",
    "dialogue": [
        {
            "id": "start",
            "text": "A sponge filter keeps water clean without too much flow. We'll rinse it gently and restart it without shocking the bacteria.",
            "options": [
                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "goto": "prep",
                    "text": "Let's prep the rinse gear",
                    "requiresItems": [
                        {
                            "id": "496b4ebb-43c8-42d7-a921-fc6ee9d6ae56",
                            "count": 1
                        },
                        {
                            "id": "60e517b4-5807-4983-afb8-e2aad1566587",
                            "count": 1
                        },
                        {
                            "id": "5d5e4e29-94b7-4a03-b73d-7420841ae686",
                            "count": 1
                        },
                        {
                            "id": "0564d441-7367-412e-b709-dad770814a39",
                            "count": 1
                        },
                        {
                            "id": "16eb261b-9d93-4aff-ab31-40f6a78d04f1",
                            "count": 1
                        },
                        {
                            "id": "997eaba9-25ee-43d5-bbdc-5d6adf03adfa",
                            "count": 1
                        }
                    ]
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "prep",
            "text": "Unplug the pump and set the filter in a bucket. Dechlorinate the rinse water so the sponge bacteria stay alive.",
            "options": [
                {
                    "type": "process",
                    "process": "condition-bucket-water",
                    "text": "Condition rinse water"
                },
                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "goto": "rinse",
                    "text": "Bucket is full of dechlorinated water",
                    "requiresItems": [
                        {
                            "id": "71efa72a-8c87-4dc2-8e2c-9119bb28fe50",
                            "count": 1
                        }
                    ]
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "rinse",
            "text": "Squeeze the sponge in the dechlorinated bucket until the flow returns but the media stays wet. Keep tubing and the pump dry and upright.",
            "options": [
                {
                    "type": "process",
                    "process": "rinse-aquarium-filter",
                    "text": "Rinse and clean the sponge core"
                },
                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "goto": "restart",
                    "text": "Sponge rinsed and still wet",
                    "requiresItems": [
                        {
                            "id": "606c4f47-ca8f-4458-bc7f-0ab2957ef641",
                            "count": 1
                        }
                    ]
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "restart",
            "text": "Reassemble, reinstall, and prime the filter. Keep the outlet pointed at the surface for gas exchange, then check bubbles are even.",
            "options": [
                {
                    "type": "process",
                    "process": "restart-sponge-filter",
                    "text": "Restart the bubbler"
                },
                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "goto": "finish",
                    "text": "Flow is restored without splashing",
                    "requiresItems": [
                        {
                            "id": "6f08e704-1086-4fef-ad0a-f48922a5cfd0",
                            "count": 1
                        }
                    ]
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "finish",
            "text": "Nice! Mark the date so you remember the next rinse, and keep a spare bucket nearby for emergencies.",
            "options": [
                {
                    "type": "finish",
                    "text": "Filter humming along"
                }
            ]
        }
    ],
    "rewards": [],
    "requiresQuests": [
        "aquaria/goldfish"
    ],
